  "description": "<i>The Serf's Tale</i> is a traditional text adventure made using a modified verison of the Quill adventure generation software from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?company=Gilsoft\">Gilsoft</a>. You tell the game what you want to do via a textual interface and the parser is based on a verb / noun input.<br><br><i>The Serf's Tale</i> is a rendition of the classic Colossal Cave Adventure by <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/developer/sheet/view/developerId,15632/\">Will Crowther</a> and <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?developer=Don+Woods\">Don Woods</a>. In this enhanced version there are 16 treasures to collect, locations have been added, existing location text added upon and the major puzzles reworked.",
